AGENDA
=======
 
The primary agenda item is approving the final edits to the C++ working
draft to be submitted for second CD ballot within SC22.  The working
draft will be in the pre-meeting mailing as well as being available
electronically, and the Project Editor will be prepared to edit the
draft during the meeting, so that a final copy may be shipped to SC22
immediately after the meeting.
 
The Disposition of Comments document will be finalized to send with the
working draft to SC22.
 
There will also be a report from the Convener on the SC22 Plenary meeting
which will have been held in September.
 
